'''阿馬'''（{{lang-en|Armagh}}，{{lang-ga|Ard Mhacha}}），[[英國|英國]][[北愛爾蘭|北愛爾蘭]][[阿馬郡|阿馬郡]][[阿馬區|阿馬區]]的[[英國城市地位|城市]]，北愛爾蘭五座[[英國城市地位|城市]]之一。羅馬天主教和聖公會的全愛爾蘭主教長、阿馬總主教均駐此，設有[[天主教|天主教]][[聖巴特利爵主教座堂_(阿馬)|聖巴特利爵主教座堂]]和[[聖公會|聖公會]][[聖帕特里克座堂_(阿馬)|聖派翠克座堂]]。

儘管被列為中型城鎮<ref name="NISRA">{{cite web |title= Settlement Information on Armagh City |url= http://www.ninis2.nisra.gov.uk/public/AreaProfileReportViewer.aspx?FromAPAddressMulipleRecords=Armagh%20City@Partial%20match%20of%20location%20name:%20@Partial%20Match%20Of%20Location%20Name:%20%20Armagh%20City@16? |publisher= Northern Ireland Neighbourhood Information Service |accessdate= 20 February 2016 |archive-date= 2016-03-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081702/http://www.ninis2.nisra.gov.uk/public/AreaProfileReportViewer.aspx?FromAPAddressMulipleRecords=Armagh%20City%40Partial%20match%20of%20location%20name%3A%20%40Partial%20Match%20Of%20Location%20Name%3A%20%20Armagh%20City%4016%3F |dead-url= no }}</ref>，但伊麗莎白二世女王還是在1994年將阿馬授予城市地位。在2011年人口普查中，它的人口為14,777人<ref name=Census2011>{{cite web | url = http://www.ninis2.nisra.gov.uk/public/AreaProfileReportViewer.aspx?FromAPAddressMulipleRecords=Armagh@Exact%20match%20of%20location%20name:%20@Exact%20Match%20Of%20Location%20Name:%20%20Armagh@23? | title = Census 2011 Population Statistics for Armagh Settlement | publisher = [[Northern_Ireland_Statistics_and_Research_Agency|Northern Ireland Statistics and Research Agency]] (NISRA) | accessdate = 15 April 2019 | archive-date = 2021-11-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211104062358/https://www.ninis2.nisra.gov.uk/public/AreaProfileReportViewer.aspx?FromAPAddressMulipleRecords=Armagh%40Exact%20match%20of%20location%20name%3A%20%40Exact%20Match%20Of%20Location%20Name%3A%20%20Armagh%4023%3F | dead-url = no }}</ref>，使它成為北愛爾蘭人口最少的城市，以及英國人口最少的城市排名第五。

